OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA bright start with plenty of
OL,6,Fsunshine. Cloud will build through the
OL,7,Fmorning, although warm, sunny spells
OL,8,Fwill continue. Staying largely dry
OL,9,Fwith just a small chance of a few
OL,10,Fshowers.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA warm end to the day with
OL,13,Fsome late evening sunshine. Staying
OL,14,Fdry overnight with clear skies at
OL,15,Ffirst, but cloudier later. A cool
OL,16,Fnight for many.
OL,17,
OL,18,CSunday:FCloudy skies are likely at
OL,19,Ffirst during the morning, but quickly
OL,20,Fturning sunny by lunchtime with blue
OL,21,Fskies and light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
